name: FastFoodChecker
0:
”Alexa, ask Fast Food Checker how many calories in a Big Mac”
”Alexa, ask Fast Food Checker how many calories in a Large Fries at Burger King”
”Alexa, ask Fast Food Checker how many calories in a Chicken Sandwich at Chick-fil-A”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: fast food checker
des:
Looking to check on how many calories are in different fast food items? Check out this skill to look up the dozens of items at your favorite restaurants. Just say 'List Restaurants' to know which menus the skill has learned. More are being added all the time!

Please Note: this skill is not sponsored or affiliated with any of these restaurants. The data for this comes directly from their public websites.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
